  "capabilities": [
    "Wrap any cron job: `cronalarm \"Job Name\" /path/to/script.sh` and the wrapper handles the rest.",
    "Timeout protection — configurable per-job (CRONALARM_TIMEOUT, default 300s). Hung jobs get killed and you get alerted.",
    "Captures stdout + stderr + exit code on every run.",
    "Multi-channel alerts on failure: Discord webhook, SMS via Textbelt, Telegram bot, local file drop. Mix and match — configure any subset.",
